## API validation rules

- Employee login validates `employeeId` exists in `data/employees.csv`.
- Admin login validates credentials from `data/admins.csv`.
- Interest submission:
  - `ticketCount` must be 1 or 2.
  - `matchIds` must be subset of hardcoded matches.
  - Store one row per `(employeeId, matchId)` in `data/interests.csv` (dedupe on re-submit).

## Draw rules

- Draw is per match and ticket-capacity aware.
- Eligible pool = interests for match minus any employeeId present in any `data/winners/*.csv`.
- Allocate by shuffled order; pick entry only if `ticketCount <= remainingTickets`.
- Winners are persisted to `data/winners/<matchId>.csv`.
- Prefer guarding against re-draw if winners file already exists and has rows.

